latestPosts.caption:
Jab Shiv aur Shakti ek roop mein milte hain, tab sirf ek kahani nahi banti... ek anubhav hota hai.

Creation begins with balance.
Shiv. Shakti. Destruction and creation—together in one form.
Presenting my first ever reel as a makeup artist, where art meets divinity.
This is just the beginning.✨
mera pehla art jisse maine apna safar shuru kiya hai.

Half face Shiv ka — tandav, vairagya, aur shanti ka prateek.
Half face Maa Parvati ka — karuna, shakti aur srijan ka roop.
Ek saath dono ban gaye ek divine balance
By posting this  reel i’m announcing 
 apna official journey — as a makeup creator, as an artist jise emotions ko colors mein badalna aata hai.

This video is incomplete without you @ashmeetkaurmakeovers 🤍🫶🏻

Please Bht saara pyaar aur blessing chaiye 
Iss new journey k liye 🙏🥹😍

ओम 🕉️ नमः पार्वती पते 
हर हर महादेव 🔱🙏❤️
